rows.label: qst104225_msg0001
rows.name:
Bzzzzzt!
A question for Mr. Rex!

rows.label: qst104225_msg0002
rows.name:
Can you find all kinds of cool treasure
in the Cloud Sea really easily?!

rows.label: qst104225_msg0021
rows.name:
I sure can! I've salvaged so much,
I could probably find treasure with
my eyes closed at this point.

rows.label: qst104225_msg0022
rows.name:
Wow! I wanna see you salvaging
sometime, Mr. Rex!

rows.label: qst104225_msg0041
rows.name:
Well, it wouldn't be that easy.
I'd probably have to salvage quite a lot
of times to find the really good stuff.

rows.label: qst104225_msg0042
rows.name:
Oh, I see.
I always thought you just dive in and
bring up amazing treasure every time!

rows.label: qst104225_msg0043
rows.name:
I've never seen you actually salvaging!
You should show me sometime!

rows.label: qst104225_msg0101
rows.name:
You're not the teacher.
Rex is the teacher.
